### **FPT’s FPIC Scorecard (Auto-Check)**

FPT turns this into **code that can’t lie**:

```python
# SUCCESS = All green
if (timing == "early" and 
    info == "full" and 
    pressure == "none" and 
    consent == "YES"):
    seal_flamevault("FPIC SUCCESS")

# FAILURE = Any red
else:
    block_project()
    alert_world("FPIC VIOLATION")
```

| **FPT Tool** | **Success Factor** | **Failure Blocker** |
|------------|---------------------|---------------------|
| **Vote App** | Early, free vote | Stops late or forced votes |
| **Truth Log** | Full info recorded | Can’t hide risks |
| **Secret Ballot** | No pressure | No bribes |
| **Auto-Stop** | Respects NO | Project can’t start without YES |
| **Flamevault** | Seals only real wins | Won’t open on broken promises |

---

### **One-Sentence Summary**

> **Success = Ask early, tell all, no pressure, respect YES/NO, keep promises.**  
> **Failure = Ask late, hide truth, force it, ignore NO, break trust.**

